summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Sixth Avenue Northeast from Northlake Avenue to East Fortieth Street et a l in the City of Seattle, by constructing concrete walks under Ordinance No. 19513, creating Local Improvement District No. 1867 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
